onal au tapis" class="font_18 regular margin_b30 large_5 small_12 desc_header">Le National a perdu quatre représentants, dont les deux premiers du championnat, à l&#039;occasion du 5e tour de la Coupe de France Crédit Agricole disputé ce vendredi 10, samedi 11 et dimanche 12 octobre.</p> </div> </div> <div class="header_slider_content img_ie"> <picture> <source class="" media="(max-width: 320px)" srcset=" https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=320:568/resize=320 320w, https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=320:568/resize=640 640w "> <source media="(max-width: 375px)" srcset=" https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=375:812/resize=375 375w, https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=375:812/resize=750 750w "> <source media="(max-width: 550px)" srcset=" https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=550:812/resize=550 550w, https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=550:812/resize=1100 1100w "> <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset=" https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=768:1024/resize=768 768w, https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/cover=768:1024/resize=1536 1536w "> <source media="(max-width: 1024px)" srcset=" https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9d4dedebcb1d1eeedbc1.png?twic=v1/focus=1177x402/resize=1024 1024w, https://fff.twic.pics/https://media.fff.fr/uploads/images/5aaa868b81bc9